0856_8ed127aae86782bd4dab5ae7b8a57baf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F160856_8ed127aae86782bd4dab5ae7b8a57baf.jpg&h=33e262d6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你去邊度shopping 多"},{"pid":"60d81d4fd84a64d5d38686c4af31d5234a757934","tid":499780,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"米蘭悶到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24965dd572db12d14b9711dfbf668e7099c977af","tid":499780,"uid":26812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>米蘭大教堂附近有黑人比飼料你餵鴿<br />\n唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n地鐵站售票機附近亦會有人會好心教你買飛<br />\n事後會問你攞錢 <br />\n點解我知 我中過伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：5月頭去完</blockquote><br />\n比人屈左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一蚊兩蚊到<br />\n建議你去到買day pass , 分左一日，幾日pass 不等<br />\n<br />\n我呢個兩日pass<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/160856_8ed127aae86782bd4dab5ae7b8a57baf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F160856_8ed127aae86782bd4dab5ae7b8a57baf.jpg&h=33e262d6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你去邊度shopping 多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我巴打黎 shopping 對我不感興趣<br />\n我去米蘭淨係去左<br />\n米蘭大教堂<br />\n聖西路<br />\n<br />\n如果你仲有少少時間既話可以去睇達文西的最後晚餐<br />\n如果官網訂要預早三個月前訂<br />\n但你可以去Expedia 到買one day tour （應該都仲有位睇）"},{"pid":"7b776208fd8779b5d36fcdf6b663e641d0abd1be","tid":499780,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"米蘭都算係係咁多意大利大城市份面最無野睇果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非你好中意shopping"},{"pid":"7bf7f2f75bea11499ba27a4115a6ea294ea2bb43","tid":499780,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"火車站果頭最危，反而D境點冇羅馬咁多捃水既黑/吉卜賽人，可能冇咁多人去米蘭撈呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b318e202dd3910705ea9e53447a48e028ff327bc","tid":499780,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去半日就夠(認真）<br />\n大教堂去一去就好<br />\n<br />\n酒店又貴又垃圾</blockquote><br />\n咁威尼斯呢</blockquote><br />\n更貴，但係值"},{"pid":"ffd37d93cf3a64e3d5bcf903efaa8b46f20b9dca","tid":499780,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去聖西路</blockquote><br />\n有咩睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有兩隊西波任睇"},{"pid":"c5931e8ebb3ebff39ba6c5919b7e46c1551e7fde","tid":499780,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去聖西路</blockquote><br />\n有咩睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有兩隊西波任睇</blockquote><br />\n國米就唔西嘅<br />\n不過球場真係好有風味，唔好聽就係舊"},{"pid":"f0d6ff1a2d58d29e1e8dde66b5bd6ed235c9f804","tid":499780,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"留名先<br />\n我一月中同女朋友去<br />\n買左飛睇最後晚餐<br />\n諗住hae遊3日<br />\n有冇咩好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648a439a64addc18d68874b12580e46fdb36aec6","tid":499780,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/182746_a818345f6c45a4